-- Support code auto completion;
-- Compile, Run Offline C++ (with STL support) Python, and terminal support;
-- Support multiply window and split screen (For iPad);

An IDE for iPad, iPhone devices. Use apple clang compiler to build and run your C/C++ code offline on your device. Also support many language edit, for other language this is a useful auto completion notepad.

Support Languages:
Edit and run: C C++ Python CDBuild(Build System Script) HTML(JavaScript+CSS)
Edit only: CSharp Swift Objective-C Objective-C++ Java
